":"Yes, zoom in CombinedCamera works fine and is controlled using links. Possibly I could assign the same behaviour to mouse wheel.\n","created_at":"2012-03-11T14:12:34.000Z","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/1454#issuecomment-4439232","id":4439232,"issue_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/1454","node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDQ0MzkyMzI=","updated_at":"2012-03-11T14:12:34.000Z","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/comments\/4439232","user":{"following_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Landlord-xx\/following{\/other_user}","events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Landlord-xx\/events{\/privacy}","avatar_url":"https:\/\/avatars3.githubusercontent.com\/u\/1392434?v=4","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Landlord-xx","gists_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Landlord-xx\/gists{\/gist_id}","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/Landlord-xx","subscriptions_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Landlord-xx\/subscriptions","node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEzOTI0MzQ=","repos_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Landlord-xx\/repos","received_events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Landlord-xx\/received_events","gravatar_id":"","starred_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Landlord-xx\/starred{\/owner}{\/repo}","site_admin":false,"login":"Landlord-xx","type":"User","id":1392434,"followers_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Landlord-xx\/followers","organizations_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Landlord-xx\/orgs"}},{"index":2,"author_association":"NONE","body":"are there any examples that actually use CombinedCamera and Trackball? Thanks. \n","created_at":"2013-04-08T15:31:02.000Z","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/1454#issuecomment-16057338","id":16057338,"issue_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/1454","node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDE2MDU3MzM4","updated_at":"2013-04-08T15:31:02.000Z","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/comments\/16057338","user":{"following_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/donbright\/following{\/other_user}","events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/donbright\/events{\/privacy}","avatar_url":"https:\/\/avatars2.githubusercontent.com\/u\/896858?v=4","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/donbright","gists_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/donbright\/gists{\/gist_id}","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/donbright","subscriptions_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/donbright\/subscriptions","node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjg5Njg1OA==","repos_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/donbright\/repos","received_events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/donbright\/received_events","gravatar_id":"","starred_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/donbright\/starred{\/owner}{\/repo}","site_admin":false,"login":"donbright","type":"User","id":896858,"followers_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/donbright\/followers","organizations_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/donbright\/orgs"}},{"index":3,"author_association":"NONE","body":"For the record, it's not easy to use `CombinedCamera` together with `TrackballControls`. I just tried it by copying and adjusting the `mousewheel` function from `TrackballControls` and listening for mousewheel events. It works somehow but in the end it's really hacky. For me, the problem is that the rotation\/pan operations act in the reverse direction with `CombinedCamera` compared to `OrthographicCamera`. It just feels not natural to control it like that. That's why I'd rather prefer to use `OrthographicCamera`.\n\nEDIT: Here's my little helper for zooming with `OrthographicCamera`:\n\n``` js\nvar zoom = 0.02;\nfunction mousewheel( event ) {\n    event.preventDefault();\n    event.stopPropagation();\n\n    var delta = 0;\n\n    if ( event.wheelDelta ) { \/\/ WebKit \/ Opera \/ Explorer 9\n        delta = event.wheelDelta \/ 40;\n    } else if ( event.detail ) { \/\/ Firefox\n        delta = - event.detail \/ 3;\n    }\n\n    var width = camera.right \/ zoom;\n    var height = camera.top \/ zoom;\n\n    zoom -= delta * 0.001;\n\n    camera.left = -zoom*width;\n    camera.right = zoom*width;\n    camera.top = zoom*height;\n    camera.bottom = -zoom*height;\n\n    camera.updateProjectionMatrix();\n\n    renderer.render( scene, camera );\n}\n```\n\nand then when initializing stuff:\n\n``` js\nvar camera = new THREE.OrthographicCamera(-zoom*width, zoom*width, zoom*height, -zoom*height, 1, 1000  );\ncamera.position.z = 100;\nrenderer.domElement.addEventListener( 'mousewheel', mousewheel, false );\nrenderer.domElement.addEventListener( 'DOMMouseScroll', mousewheel, false ); \/\/ firefox\n\nvar controls = new THREE.TrackballControls( camera );\n...\ncontrols.noZoom = true; \/\/ important!\n```\n","created_at":"2013-06-02T17:08:39.000Z","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/1454#issuecomment-18809633","id":18809633,"issue_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/1454","node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDE4ODA5NjMz","updated_at":"2013-06-02T17:38:33.000Z","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/comments\/18809633","user":{"following_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/letmaik\/following{\/other_user}","events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/letmaik\/events{\/privacy}","avatar_url":"https:\/\/avatars1.githubusercontent.com\/u\/530988?v=4","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/letmaik","gists_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/letmaik\/gists{\/gist_id}","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/letmaik","subscriptions_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/letmaik\/subscriptions","node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjUzMDk4OA==","repos_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/letmaik\/repos","received_events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/letmaik\/received_events","gravatar_id":"","starred_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/letmaik\/starred{\/owner}{\/repo}","site_admin":false,"login":"letmaik","type":"User","id":530988,"followers_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/letmaik\/followers","organizations_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/letmaik\/orgs"}},{"index":4,"author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"I just came across this issue, as well. `CombinedCamera` does not handle `TrackballControls` well, so I have a `PerspectiveCamera` and an `OrthographicCamera` instantiated that I switch between.\n\n@neothemachine nice helper function! In my particular use, I didn't have easy access to event listeners, so I edited `TrackballControls.js`. In `TrackballControls.zoomCamera`, replace `_eye.multiplyScalar( factor );` with \n\n``` javascript\nif ( this.object instanceof THREE.PerspectiveCamera ) {\n\n    _eye.multiplyScalar( factor );\n\n} else {\n\n    this.object.left *= factor;\n    this.object.right *= factor;\n    this.object.top *= factor;\n    this.object.bottom *= factor;\n\n    this.object.updateProjectionMatrix();\n}\n```\n\nIf someone more familiar with the source thinks this is an okay edit, I would love to see it committed.\n","created_at":"2013-06-09T19:29:33.000Z","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/1454#issuecomment-19171895","id":19171895,"issue_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/1454","node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDE5MTcxODk1","updated_at":"2013-06-09T19:29:33.000Z","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/comments\/19171895","user":{"following_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/patrickfuller\/following{\/other_user}","events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/patrickfuller\/events{\/privacy}","avatar_url":"https:\/\/avatars3.githubusercontent.com\/u\/1449833?v=4","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/patrickfuller","gists_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/patrickfuller\/gists{\/gist_id}","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/patrickfuller","subscriptions_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/patrickfuller\/subscriptions","node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0NDk4MzM